最后一场国家队比赛。数据显示目前郑智为国家队出场的纪录是 108 场。 在联赛中，郑智最后一次出场是 2022 年 1 月 1 日 2021 赛季中超第 21 轮广州队和长春亚泰队的比赛，2022 赛季郑智虽然仍旧进入球队名单，但没有出场比赛。2023 年，扬科维奇接手国足后，郑智担任中国国家队助理教练。 因为疫情的原因，国足上一次在主场征战国际比赛，还是 2021 年 5 月在苏州对阵关岛队的世预赛亚洲区 40 强赛，那时郑智还在踢球，在郑智任教后，国足一直没有主场比赛，也就没能给他一个仪式。作为功勋队长，同时作为国家队助理教练，中国足协在 6 月 16 日为郑智举行退役仪式，自然是非常适宜且暖心的，更见证着中国足球人的延续和传承。足球报：16 日对阵缅甸，国足将为郑智举行退役仪式"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a3f622518356af6dfd4b0503ff6a0acc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606133754"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IybTz58GnmtVZEAMaCDk2OTc2NTQ3ILuMmqQGMAA4HUAKcgg5Njk3NjU0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1686723026.641322", "card_id": "Q_472271524", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "请问我国现代诗成就最高的诗人是谁？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "读过艾青、穆旦、北岛、舒婷、张枣、多多、杨炼、顾城、海子…"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472271524"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IybTz58GnmtVZEAMaCDY3MjI4NjU0IKL8u4cGMAA4kgFAC3IINjcyMjg2NTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1686723026.641803", "card_id": "Q_606543951", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_ar